Package: vtk
Title: System Dependencies for the Visualization Toolkit (VTK)
Version: 9.5.2
Authors@R: c(
    person(
        given = "Aymeric",
        family = "Stamm",
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        email = "aymeric.stamm@cnrs.fr",
        comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8725-3654")
    ))
Description: Provides pre-compiled static VTK libraries and headers for
    Windows; on macOS and Linux it locates a system-installed VTK. Downstream
    packages can declare 'Imports: vtk' and obtain the correct compiler and
    linker flags at install time via 'vtk::CppFlags()' and 'vtk::LdFlags()'.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
URL: https://github.com/astamm/vtk
BugReports: https://github.com/astamm/vtk/issues
SystemRequirements: VTK (>= 9.1.0) on macOS and Linux. On Windows, pre-built
    static libraries are downloaded automatically from
    <https://github.com/astamm/vtk/releases>.
NeedsCompilation: no
